      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Papers of the U.S. Postal Service employee and poet. Correspondence (1940-1976); scrapbooks 
relating to the Postal Services' Suggestions Program to which Kalugin submitted over 500 suggestions (1963-1976); 
manuscript and/or published novels, poems, and short stories.</abstract>
